         <ab/>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <note>The following division into weekdays and the texts of the prayers are taken from
               <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref> unless indicated otherwise.</note>
             
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Introduction">
               <label>Introduction</label>
               <ab>በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                  ንጽሕፍ፡ መቅድመ፡ ሰይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዘ፯ ዕለታት፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ብክሙ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በከመ፡ አተውክሙ፡
                  ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ አብርሃም፡</ab>
               <note>quoted after <ref type="mss" target="ESktm012"/></note>
            </div>
            
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Monday">
               <label>Praise for Monday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Enaqqeh">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Monday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> 
                        እነቅህ፨ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፤ እትነሣእ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፤ አአምን፨ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፤</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Mahtama">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Monday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/SACEth002">Cairo, Société d’Archéologie Copte, Éthiopien 002</ref>. The following incipit and explicit are
                     given according to <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/SACEth002">Cairo, Société d’Archéologie Copte, Éthiopien 002</ref>.</note>
               
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>ዝንቱ፡ ስመ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ግሩም፡ ማኅተመ፡ ሕይወት፡ ለምዕመናን፨ ወማኅተመ፡ መንሱት፡ ለረሲዓን፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>በዝንቱ፡ ስመ፡ ሥላሴ፡ <gap reason="illegible"/>ማኅፀን፡ ከመ፡ ይክፍሉኒ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡
                        ደብተራ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Aatteb">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Monday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/SACEth002">Cairo, Société d’Archéologie Copte, Éthiopien 002</ref>. The following incipit and explicit are
                     given according to <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/SACEth002">Cairo, Société d’Archéologie Copte, Éthiopien 002</ref>.</note>
                     
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፡ አአምን፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፡ እትመኃፀን፨
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፨ በቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ አአምን፡ ወእትመኃፀን፡ እክህድከ፡ ሰይጣን፨ ለዓመ፡ ዓለ፡ አሜን፨ 
                      አአትብ፡ ገጽየ፡ በምዕዛረ፡ ገጹ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፨
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>አአትብ፡ ዘመንየ፡ በምዕዛረ፡ ዘመኑ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአልቦ፡ ጥንት፡ ወኢተፍጻሚት፡ ለዓለመ፡ አሜን፨</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="SalamMonday">
                  <note>Part of the prayer for Monday, the first verse is identical in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient525">London, British Library, BL Oriental 525</ref>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>, then possibly diverging.</note>
                  <ab>ሰላም፡ ለአብ፡ ነቅዓ፡ ዘይት፡ ምሕርት፡ ጥሉል።</ab>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerMonday"> 
                  <note>Part of the prayer for Monday, following <ref target="#SalamMonday"/>. The beginning in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient525">London, British Library, BL Oriental 525</ref>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref> is not identical, but very similar.</note>
                  <ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>
                     መለኮተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ፍጽምት፡ አሐቲ፡ ስምረት፡ ወሠለስቱ፡ <del rend="erasure"/>
                     አካል፡ በዋህድ፡ ጽምረት፡ ፩ መንበር፡ በ፩ ህላዌ፡</ab>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Babahreya">
                  <note>Described as explicit of <ref target="#Enaqqeh"/> as prayer for Monday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>, 
                     transmitted for Tuesday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ANLcr53">Rome, Biblioteca dell’Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei, Conti Rossini 53</ref>. The following complete text is
                     given according to <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>, where it is transmitted for Monday.</note>
                  
                     <ab>
                        አአምን፡ አንሰ፡ በባሕርየ፡ ስሙ፡ ለአብ፡ ዘይሴባሕ፡ ቦቱ፡ ወልድ፡ ወይትዌደስ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አአምን፡ አንሰ፡ በባሕርየ፡ ስሙ፡ ለወልድ፡ ዘይትቄደስ፡ ቦቱ፡ አብ፡ ወይትባረክ፡ ቦቱ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                        አአምን፡ አንሰ፡ በባሕርየ፡ ስሙ፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘኅቡረ፡  ተአኵቶ፡
                        ምስለ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ዘንተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ 
                        አአምን፡ ወአትመኃፀን፡ እክህደከ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </ab>
               </div>
               
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Tuesday">
               <label>Praise for Tuesday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Fesmeya">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Tuesday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>ኦአብ፡ ፍጽምየ፨ በመለኮተ፡ ስሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ አኃትም፡ ከዋላየ፡ በመለኮተ፤ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አኃትም፡ የማንየ፡ በመለኮተ፤ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አኃትም፡ ጸጋምየ፡ በመለኮተ፤ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <note>The following explicit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>.</note>
                    <ab> አኃትም፡ ፍናውየ፡ ወህላዌየ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይቅረቡኒ፡ መናፍስት፡ ርኩሳን፡ ወበዝ፡ ዓለም፡ በሕይወትየ፡ ወበዘይመጽእ፡
                    ዓለም፡ እምድኅረ፡ ሞትየ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</ab>
                     </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="EsaggedLaAb">
                  <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>እሰግድ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለ፫ ፩ ወለዝ ፩ ፫ ቱ፡ እንበለ፡ ብዕድና፡ በሥላሴ፡ ግፅዋን፡ ወእኁዛን፡
                     በሥልጣን፡ አብ፡ በገጹ፡ ፩ ውእቱ፡ ምስለ፡ ወልድ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>እንዘ፡ ንብል፡ ቡሩክ፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወቡሩክ፡ ወልድ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቡሩክ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ፍጹመ፡ ናመልክ፡ ቦቱ፡
                     ወናመልክ፡ ሎቱ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sellusan">
                  <note>Transmitted as part of the prayers for Tuesday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref> most manuscripts
                     and as prayer of Wednesday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ANLcr53">Rome, Biblioteca dell’Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei, Conti Rossini 53</ref>.
                     The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሥሉሳን፡ በገጽ፡ ኅቡራን፡ በራዕይ፡ ወበገጽ፡ ግጽዋን፡
                        በስም፡ ዕሩያን፡ በመንግሥት፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>ወጽልመትሰ፡ ኡይረክቦ፡ ወኢይቀርቦ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ቃል፡ ቡሩክ፡ ዘአስተርአያ፡ ለማርያም፡ በአምሳለ፡ ገብርኤል፡
                     መልዓክ፡ ከማሁ፡ አስተርአየኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Akal">
                  <note>
                     The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm012">Bǝḥerāwi Kǝllǝlāwi Mangǝśti Tǝgrāy, Kadiḥ Dabra Tawāḥǝdo Qǝddǝst Māryām, KTM-012</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፫ አካል፡ ፩ መለኮት፡ እሙንቱ፡ ኢየሐፅፁ፡ ወኢይፈደፍዱ፡ ኢይውኅዱ፡
                     ወኢይበዝኁ፡ ኢይትፈለጡ፡ ወኢይበዓዱ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>በዝንቱ፡ ህላዌ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ወአማኅፀንኩ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ከመ፡ ያሥጥሙኒ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በቀላየ፡
                        ምሕረቶሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Wednesday">
               <label>Praise for Wednesday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Hebura">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Wednesday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ኅቡረ፡ ሀልዎቶሙ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በተገጽዎቶሙ፤ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በጽማሬ፡ ሥሉስ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>በዝንቱ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ኅቡር፤ ተማህፀንኩ፡ ወአማህፀንኩ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ከመ፤ ይምሐሩኒ፡ ወይሣሃሉኒ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በእንተ፡ ሥላሴሁ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገበርከ፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Thursday">
               <label>Praise for Thursday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Bagessawe">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Thursday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በግጻዌ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በሥላሴ፡ ዋህድ፡ አምላክ፡ ፫አዕማደ፡ ብርሃን፡ ፩አምጣኖሙ፡ ወ፩ስኖሙ፡ ፫መባርቅት፡ 
                        ፩ንጥረ፡ መለኮት፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>በዝንቱ፡ ስመ፡ ሥላሴ። ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ከመ፡ ይክፍለነ፤ ለሥሉሥ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እምተሳትፎ፡ ቅዱሳን፤ እንተ፤ ይእቲ፡ ደብተራ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ጽዮን፡ ለገብርከ፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Friday">
               <label>Praise for Friday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="AyLessan">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Friday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አይ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ዘይክል፤ ነቢበ፡ ዕበየ፡ ክብሩ፡ ለሥላሴ፤ አይ፤ ልቡና፤ ወአይ፡ ሰሚዕ፡ ዘይክል፡ አእምሮ፤ ህላዌሁ፡ ለስላሴ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ጠቢብ፡ በምክሩ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ 
                        ሰብእ፡ ወመላእክት፡ 
                        ዘኢየአምርዎ፤
                        ለምክሩ፡ ወለምሥጢሩ፤ ለዓለመ፤ ዓለም፤ አሜን፨</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Saturday">
               <label>Praise for Saturday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="FeqraMalakot" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2933RepCh214">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Saturday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>ሰላም፡ ለፍቅረ፡ መለኮት፤ በትስብእቱ፤ ዘጾመ፡ እንበይነ፡ ዚአሁ፡ አርአያሁ፤ ከመ፡ የሀበነ፤ ሰላም፡ ለፍቅረ፡ መለኮት፡ ዘይጼአን፡ ላዕለ፡ 
                        ኪሩቤል፡ በትስብእቱ፡ ተፅዕነ፡ ዲበ፡ ዕዋል፤</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>ግናይ፡ ወቡራኬ፤ ስባሔ፡ ወዝማሬ፡ ይደሉ፡ ለሥላሴ፡ በሰማይ፤ ወበምድር፡ በየብስ፡ ወበባሕር፤ ዲበ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፍጡር፡ ወግቡር፡ ላዕለ፡ ክሡት፤ ወስውር፨ መባሕተ፡ 
                        ኩነኔ፡ ይደሉ፡ መለኮት፤
                        አብ፤ ወወልድ፤ ወመንፈስ፤ ቅዱስ፤ ለገብርከ፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Daily">
               <label>Praise for every day (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘዘወትር፡</foreign>
               </label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Yetbarak">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for every day in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ወላዴ፡ ወልድ፡ ቅዱስ፤ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወልድ፡ አብ፡ ዋህድ፡ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጰራቅሊጦስ፡ መንፈሰ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>ስብሐት፡ ለሥላሴ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለሥላሴ፡ ምልዕት፡ በኵለሄ፤ ለሥላሴ፡ ይደሉ፡ ስባሄ፡ ሥላሴ፤ ዕውቅ፤ በሱራኄ፡ አድኅኖ፡ 
                        ወዕቀቦ፡ ለገብርከ፤</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sunday">
               <label>Praise for Sunday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Ahasses">
                  <note>Transmitted as prayer for Sunday in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet89">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 89</ref>.</note>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                     <ab>አኃሥሥ፡ ጽቅቀ።
                        እምኀቤከ፡ ኦቀመረ፡ ጽድቅ፡ አኃሥሥ፡ ጥበበ፡ እምኔከ፡ ኦሙዳየ፤ ጥበብ፡</ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                     <ab>ወበደኃሪት፤ ዕለት፡ ትባልሕ፡ እሞት፤ ወታወርስ፡ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፤ ለገብርከ፡</ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text></TEI>